description: The cavalry, when they arrived, came in style: one by one, the six private jets landed at German airport Erfurt-Weimar, at an estimated cost of over £400,000.
title: It's WAG war! Fed up with 'publicity seeking' Annie Kilner, how the others are 'drawing the line', says KATIE HIND, as insiders tell of 'nightmare' of Kyle and her marital dramas - and fury when it was found exactly who was leaking it all...

description: Emerald Fennell's cult film Saltburn is a disturbing satire of upper-class life. Now, the Oscar-winning director's father, Theo Fennell, has revealed the extent of his own family's dysfunction.
title: RICHARD EDEN: Jeweller Fennell's most unusual snub to his late mother

description: The former Oasis star, 57, has been struggling with the joint problem, it was reported on Friday.
title: Noel Gallagher, 57, 'set to undergo surgery for a knee replacement after being hit by arthritis' - just months after his younger brother Liam had a hip operation for the same condition

description: The girl group have just finished up their 20th anniversary reunion tour, which finished with an exclusive O2 Priority gig in London.
title: Glastonbury organiser Emily Eavis 'is hoping to book Girls Aloud for next year's festival' - after pop princesses Sugababes and Avril Lavigne drew huge crowds
